<font color="#FF0000">MTF'S FIRST JUMP</font><br>
<tt>Mon Dec 15  1:43:16 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
A new Airborne paratrooper by the name of Mustang Two Four was making his first jump: his instructor OD_Green as the story goes, told MTF which cord on the harness to pull after he was out of the aircraft. <br><br>
He also told him that after he landed, SW would be sitting in an Army jeep waiting to take him back to the base.<br><br>
MTF jumped, but wheen he pulled the ripcord nothing mhappened.<br>
He complained,<br>
&quot;And I bet the jeep won't be there, either.&quot;<br><br>
Thank you Bob Hope for the joke<br><br>
Sparrowhawk
